17 needed integrations, reducing cost and effort to do that work while
18 increasing data accuracy and usability.
19 (c) Promoting the use of a more common set of applications by
20 promoting systems that integrate with the Michigan data hub
21 network.
22 (d) Promoting 100% district adoption of the Michigan data hub
23 network.
24 (e) Ensuring local control of data, data security, and student
