12 committee. The primary focus of the committee is to recommend tools
13 and strategies with the goal of increasing student academic
14 outcomes in the area of literacy. The committee is encouraged to
15 collaborate with the Michigan Education Research Institute or other
16 entities with similar expertise on the subject of literacy. The
17 department shall determine the size , timeline, and benchmarks of
18 the committee. The committee shall do all of the following:
19 (a) Critically evaluate early literacy series and materials.
